the American Folklife Center here

00:00:34.080 --> 00:00:37.360
at the Library of Congress
and I want to welcome you

00:00:37.360 --> 00:00:41.320
to the latest presentation in the
Botkin [phonetic] lecture series.

00:00:41.320 --> 00:00:46.220
