00:04:01.560 --> 00:04:03.390
which I think is a fairly recent --

00:04:03.390 --> 00:04:04.690
&gt;&gt; As of today.

00:04:04.690 --> 00:04:05.990
&gt;&gt; Degree, okay.

00:04:05.990 --> 00:04:07.290
Congratulations.

00:04:07.290 --> 00:04:09.640
And he has also taught
